-4109115.jpg','images/thumbnail/1761648612_pexels-polina-tankilevitch-4109115.jpg','2025-10-28 10:50:12','2025-10-28 10:50:12'),(40,71,'Cheeseburger','Description: Grilled beef patty with cheese, lettuce, and tomato on a toasted bun.',8.00,'images/original/1761648715_pexels-enginakyurt-2282532 (1).jpg','images/thumbnail/1761648715_pexels-enginakyurt-2282532 (1).jpg','2025-10-28 10:51:55','2025-10-28 10:51:55'),(41,71,'Club Sandwich','Description: Triple-decker sandwich filled with chicken, egg, and fresh vegetables.',7.00,'images/original/1761648804_pexels-alexravvas-28681955 (1).jpg','images/thumbnail/1761648804_pexels-alexravvas-28681955 (1).jpg','2025-10-28 10:53:24','2025-10-28 10:53:24'),(42,72,'Chocolate Cake','Description: Rich chocolate cake topped with smooth frosting.',6.50,'images/original/1761648899_pexels-elli-559179-1854652 (1).jpg','images/thumbnail/1761648899_pexels-elli-559179-1854652 (1).jpg','2025-10-28 10:54:59','2025-10-28 10:54:59');
